<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> For the purpose of granting the Community financial support referred to in Article 1, the Commission shall take the necessary steps to apply this Regulation, in agreement with the Member States involved and taking into account the amounts estimated to be necessary. </inglise>
